
@startuml

' Define main classes
class Aircraft {
    +name: String
    +type: String
    +yearOfManufacture: int
    +nextInspectionDate: Date
}

class PassengerAircraft {
    +numberOfSeats: int
}

class Flight {
    +flightNumber: String
    +date: Date
}

class Passenger {
    +name: String
    +passportNumber: String
}

class Ticket {
    +ticketNumber: String
    +price: float
    +upgradeDesired: boolean
}

class SeatCategory {
    +designation: String
    +entertainmentAvailable: boolean
    +numberOfSeats: int
}

class Airline {
    +name: String
}

class CrewMember {
    +name: String
    +dateOfEmployment: Date
}

class Pilot extends CrewMember {
    +license: String
}

class FlightAttendant extends CrewMember {
    +isChiefSteward: boolean
}

class Airport {
    +name: String
    +address: String
    +numberOfRunways: int
}

' Relationships
Aircraft <|-- PassengerAircraft
PassengerAircraft "1" *-- "many" SeatCategory : has
Flight "1" *-- "many" Passenger : includes
Flight "1" *-- "many" Ticket : has
Ticket "1" *-- "1" SeatCategory : belongs to
Passenger "1" *-- "many" Ticket : owns
PassengerAircraft "0..1" --> "1" Aircraft : is a type of
Aircraft "0..1" --> "1" Airline : belongs to
Airline "1" *-- "many" Pilot : employs
Airline "1" *-- "many" FlightAttendant : employs
Flight "1" *-- "1" Pilot : has as captain
Flight "1" *-- "2" Pilot : has as co-pilot (optional)
Flight "1" *-- "many" FlightAttendant : has crew
Flight "1" --> "1" Aircraft : operated by
Flight "1" --> "1" Airport : departs from
Flight "1" --> "1" Airport : arrives at
Airport "0..1" --> "1" Aircraft : is home airport for

@enduml

---

### Notes:
- **Inheritance**: `PassengerAircraft` inherits from `Aircraft`.
- **Multiplicity**:
  - A flight can have multiple passengers and tickets.
  - A ticket is linked to one seat category.
  - An aircraft may or may not be part of an airline.
  - A pilot may be the captain or a co-pilot in a flight.
- **Roles**: Specific roles like chief steward are modeled with attributes.
- **Associations**:
  - Flights are associated with departure and destination airports.
  - Pilots and flight attendants are employed by airlines.
  - Each passenger aircraft has several seat categories.

